Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:04.31,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.66,0:00:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle between Imperial \NArms users is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:09.02,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:18.33,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Controlling eight dead bodies \Nis tough, so she'll be sluggish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:19.99,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,I won't waste this opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:37.72,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,N-Natala...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:41.56,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Return him to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.81,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he a friend you grew up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:46.23,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:51.17,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:53.54,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I want to always be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:57.07,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I'll add you to my collection, as well, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:01.24,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,That way, we can be together, like long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:03.54,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:06.76,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.80,Default - italics,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,Magma Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.63,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,That Imperial Arms also \Nhas a long-ranged attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.06,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush in alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:22.97,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Akame!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:25.81,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:32.77,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,They don't seem like an enemy \Nwe can easily defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.50,Title1a,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1485,1)}Kill the Puppets
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:08.33,Title1b,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,518)}Kill the Puppets
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:08.91,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.54,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed us and joined the likes of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.74,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Get them, Destaghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:32.73,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a mega-class Danger Beast's strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.23,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:38.19,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,The landscape's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:39.48,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hand it to the notorious Night Raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:45.91,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,You all dodged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.28,Default - italics,Lubbok,0000,0000,0000,,The battle's begun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:55.45,Default - italics,Lubbok,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do my part, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:56.64,Default - italics,Lubbok,0000,0000,0000,,Najenda...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:02.30,Default - italics,Lubbok,0000,0000,0000,,After this is over, maybe I'll \Nconfess my feelings to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.99,Default - italics,Lubbok,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't act soon, \NSu might take her from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:10.02,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,What destructive power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.70,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll stop him together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:15.76,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,That command is a mistake, Najenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:18.65,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,He is certainly powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.30,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.34,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,I can deal with him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.28,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,Have everyone else go after the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.91,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of my Imperial Arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.08,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,If I could only take down Kurome...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.31,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll snipe you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.75,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,A gun user, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:45.72,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.08,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a Danger Beast's carcass, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.44,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a type I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.40,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Another enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.42,Default,Henter,0000,0000,0000,,Unskilled... Skilled... Skilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.39,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If my armor hadn't protected \Nme, he would've gotten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.74,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.13,Default,Henter,0000,0000,0000,,I failed... Failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:23.63,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,That fire is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.21,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,I will finish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.30,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,To come straight at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.10,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Murasame is useless \Nagainst a corpse puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.03,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Akame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:45.40,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:59.00,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, you've sure done it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.49,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I can see through moves like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:06.45,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.86,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,My kinetic perception can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.72,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't even using an Imperial Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:14.31,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:17.76,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's a battle royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.81,Default,Kruome,0000,0000,0000,,How fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.06,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Kurome...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:23.73,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,See? Aren't my toys great?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.78,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Doya is an assassin from \Nthe northern tribes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:31.90,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,She's super confident. \NYou can tell by the expression on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.42,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Wall was a famous guardsman, \Nbut he was protecting my target,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:42.53,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Ape-man is a meat-head, but he's easy \Nto use, so he's one of my favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:46.29,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Henter was a survivor from the savage tribes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:49.09,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,His moves are tricky, so I had \Na tough time killing him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.43,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,He's my pride and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.53,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Rokugoh was a former general for the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.85,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,He's a traitor, who tried to join the \NRevolutionary Army, so I assassinated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:01.13,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I found Destaghoul while he was hibernating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.35,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I sure was lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.44,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.03,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Natala is a childhood friend of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:10.70,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,While I use Yatsufusa, he protects me flawlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:15.57,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have another, but you'll \Nhave to wait a bit for the debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:19.83,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one we haven't even seen yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.42,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.78,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:27.83,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.09,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,They're puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.26,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you pierce his heart, he'll keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.72,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,That is, of course, unless you defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.65,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You're certainly strong, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:44.91,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.84,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I've adjusted to it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:51.60,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Using the same move, over and \Nover, won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.20,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let go, Leone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.41,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,General Rokugoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.39,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,As my former colleague...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:03.98,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,I will free you from this spell \Nas quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.92,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's been a while since \NI've seen the boss fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.09,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,All right, my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:22.02,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't good to take your eyes off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:25.35,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,If I see an opportunity, \NI'll mercilessly attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.85,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You've done it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.19,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.97,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,As far as opportunistic attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.49,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,it's the same for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:45.17,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Stopping the bleeding \Nby yourself is impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:53.26,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what happens\N when you enrage a lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.34,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush in, Leone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.04,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Kurome has guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.35,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,First, support Akame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:05.14,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,After that, go after Kurome together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.61,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,This battle is between former generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.66,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even have an \NImperial Arms. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:12.67,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:15.98,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.82,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:22.49,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to want you in my collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:32.17,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,We should have caught up to them \Nby now. There's something off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.08,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,It is, indeed, strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.48,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be a setup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.39,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps their main target \Nwas Kurome and the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:47.56,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,So this territory is overrun by a gang of thieves...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.44,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't appear to be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.90,Default,Thieves,0000,0000,0000,,They came, exactly as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.33,Default,Thieves,0000,0000,0000,,It's General Esdeath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.36,Default,Thieves,0000,0000,0000,,She's irresistible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:57.44,Default,Seryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Then they must be cohorts of Night Raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.18,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,Seryu, Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.80,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to trample them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.63,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,Leave two or three alive but unable to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.92,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I would like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.19,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,I can't jump in carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:14.30,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:22.22,Default - italics,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,She's seeking a gap to strike while moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:25.18,Default - italics,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,I'll create that gap for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:30.69,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:38.77,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,He's even armored there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.03,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,It's specifically designed for Murasame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:44.95,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,What an insane way to dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:53.96,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:58.48,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,Akame, why did you join\N the Revolutionary Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.78,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,If we had remained as allies,\N it would have been reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:20.35,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Because my heart decided \Nthat this was the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.12,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,I merely chose to walk the path I believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.26,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:27.59,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:29.08,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:34.13,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,Incinerating you, along \Nwith that belief, is my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.11,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in on this, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.47,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's two against two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.09,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Leone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.30,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.76,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on the battle for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.03,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,They're strong. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.06,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.66,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Let's defeat Bols, \Nand head straight for Kurome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.40,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the wound Esdeath gave me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:01.32,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,my strength is only about forty \Npercent of the normal amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.78,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,I can move more than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:11.29,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,That's Earth Shaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.84,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware of your moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.38,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,They've been ingrained in me from training!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.89,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Reel Assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.65,Default - flashback,Rakugoh,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for a drink, Naje!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:50.87,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just how grossly does this Imperial Arms \Nattempt to desecrate people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:22.92,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're both pretty tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.54,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's rotting, it's still a mega-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:26.87,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, it's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.65,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.46,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look, Najenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.71,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,That protrusion bothers me very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.71,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,That area is asymmetrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:42.60,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, I was hit because I was \Npaying too much attention to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:43.59,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:47.38,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so impressive, \Nbut simultaneously, so bizarre?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:51.70,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, if someone doesn't \Nreach Kurome soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.27,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,there may actually be a casualty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:58.20,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Susanoo! As your master, \NI authorize the use of your secret ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:00.06,Default,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.07,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Their coordinated attacks are dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.41,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If one of them slowed down, for even a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.29,Default,Henter,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ally...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:38.52,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as Akame said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.96,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,The dead bodies that Yatsufusa controls
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't have their own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:47.15,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,But deep-seated habits and \Nstrong emotions remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:52.99,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, I'm not one \Nof your allies that has perished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.70,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.38,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't be able to move further.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.65,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me, Chelsea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.83,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the monkey to you, Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:14.92,Default - italics,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,That plan was pretty bold, even for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:19.10,Default - italics,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can call Sheele \Nor Bulat failures anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:24.93,Default - italics,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Later, I'll have the one who made me feel \Nthis way take responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.15,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only you, this'll be simple. \NI already know your moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.28,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Using dead people as your toys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.95,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What a repulsive Imperial Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.26,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:52.97,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, it feels like my snack \Ntime has been shortened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.68,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Wave is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:03.19,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty stubborn, so I'm sure he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.25,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.79,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Rokugoh and Henter aren't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.15,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Ape-man, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:12.27,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.65,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,The eighth should soon start to move, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.57,Default - italics,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go again, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.90,Default - italics,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,What an intense attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.63,Default - italics,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't blocked it with Grand Chariot, \NI'd have died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.99,Default - italics,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't hurry, Bols and Kurome will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:35.26,Default - italics,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,She's strong but there's something \Nspontaneous about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:38.00,Default - italics,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Almost childlike...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.26,Default - italics,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.60,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:46.01,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far was I launched?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:52.11,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretty skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.11,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,But you're up against the wrong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.24,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a genius marksman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.00,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.32,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:07.04,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're already being attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:10.20,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kaiser Frog. He's new.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:14.23,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,He's a dangerous frog whose stomach \Nacid can disintegrate anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:20.65,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Seryu that Coro ate your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.64,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means you'll die a similar death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.40,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like hell, I'm going to die
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.35,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:35.79,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,The end of life is always brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.40,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:41.27,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. We'll move on to—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.57,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:46.06,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're Akame's sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't mean I'll go easy on you, Kurome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.81,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:55.67,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,But Natala is ten times \Nstronger than that ape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.18,Default - italics,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Soul Manifestation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.18,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Susanoo's hidden ability is "Madman."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:08.75,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,With his chest, he sucks the \Nlife force from his master,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.77,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,and manifests that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:13.88,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,If used three times, it will certainly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.73,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,be the death of the master,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.08,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but the power he gains is tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:28.54,Default - italics,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror of Yata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.27,Default - italics,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering Clouds of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.44,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even in Incursio, he's as strong as I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.82,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, maybe even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.95,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Everything seems to be going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:09.67,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.41,Default,Kruome,0000,0000,0000,,She's struggling inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.49,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,But the potent stomach acid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.59,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, he's leaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.17,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.24,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,That was the worst experience ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:44.05,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.30,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,I was in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.46,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, damn it! For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.87,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,And don't look this way, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.25,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're being unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:54.00,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it at that, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:56.42,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,The battle isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.54,Default,Mine,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:01.06,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? Su, you look awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:04.13,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,You wondered how many would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:06.51,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, Kurome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:09.56,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.08,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:15.15,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you all, here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:18.45,Default,Kurome,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe I'll have you all become my puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.42,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:26.08,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:31.99,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,But they can't escape by air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.88,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.22,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.91,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of whether \Nthe guard gets in my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:45.64,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,we'll outsmart them, \Nand get rid of him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.01,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.56,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You're paying too much \Nattention to Akame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.85,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,That guard can't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.09,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.57,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.49,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,A hidden lance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.03,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,My arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:20.80,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, I can't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.51,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,She bit off my Imperial Arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:28.84,Default,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:32.22,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use your Imperial \NArms anymore, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.85,Default - italics,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.23,Default - italics,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.47,Default - italics,Bols,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:46.86,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:40.98,Title2,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,1)}Kill the Curse
